y-is-flight-minus-the-cocaine-denzel-and-fun |work=''The Daily Beast'' |accessdate=2017-08-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909222707/http://www.thedailybeast.com/clint-eastwoods-sully-is-flight-minus-the-cocaine-denzel-and-fun |archivedate=2017-09-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="The Atlantic (2016-09-09)">{{cite web |last1=Orr |first1=Christopher |date=2016-09-09 |title=The Silliness of Sully |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/09/the-silliness-of-sully/499247/ |work=''The Atlantic'' |accessdate=2017-08-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818175023/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/09/the-silliness-of-sully/499247/ |archivedate=2017-08-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|麥克·拉帕波特|Michael Rapaport}}、{{link-en|傑夫·科伯|Jeff Kober}}、{{link-en|莫莉·貝爾納|Molly Bernard}}與[[克里斯·鮑爾|克里斯·鮑爾]]分飾酒保彼特（{{lang|en|Pete}}）、L·T·庫克（{{lang|en|L. T. Cook}}）、愛莉森（{{lang|en|Alison}}）與賴瑞·魯尼（{{lang|en|Larry Rooney}}）<ref name="IMDb-Cast">{{cite web |title=Sully (2016) Full Cast & Crew |url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3263904/fullcredits?ref_=tt_cl_sm#cast |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2018-06-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919012212/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3263904/fullcredits?ref_=tt_cl_sm#cast |archivedate=2017-09-19}}</ref>。曾參與該事故的救援行動的渡輪船長文森·彼得·倫巴迪（{{lang|en|Vincent Peter Lombardi}}）參演了電影，飾演他本人<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/><ref name="THR (2016-09-09)">{{cite web |last1=Giardina |first1=Carolyn |date=2016-09-09 |title=‘Sully’ Cinematographer Reveals How Clint Eastwood Landed a Plane in the Hudson River |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/sully-cinematographer-how-clint-eastwood-925205 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2018-05-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008114408/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/sully-cinematographer-how-clint-eastwood-925205 |archivedate=2017-10-08}}</ref>。電影中的部分救難人員及警員由真正的救難人