== 製作 ==

2010年，製片人[[法蘭克·馬歇爾|法蘭克·馬歇爾]]與艾琳·史都華（{{lang|en|Allyn Stewart}}）取得了[[切斯利·蘇倫柏格|切斯利·「薩利」·蘇倫柏格]]的回憶錄《{{link-en|最高職責 (小說)|Highest Duty: My Search for What Really Matters|最高職責}}》的電影改編權<ref name="JuneTHR">{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Clint Eastwood's Next Movie Revealed: Capt. "Sully" Sullenberger Tale (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/clint-eastwoods-next-movie-revealed-799151|accessdate=2015-06-19|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|date=2015-06-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807164635/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/clint-eastwoods-next-movie-revealed-799151|archivedate=2017-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。起初，他們曾擔心該書籍是否能改編成電影，因該故事早已廣為大眾所知<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。他們與奇普·尼爾森（{{lang|en|Kipp Nelson}}）一同構思劇本<ref name="screenplay">{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |date=2016-12-21 |title=‘Sully’ Producers On A Film That Almost Didn’t Take Flight |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/sully-frank-marshall-allyn-stewart-tim-moore-producers-oscars-interview-1201871653/ |publisher=Deadline.com |accessdate=2017-02-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025042407/http://deadline.com/2016/12/sully-frank-marshall-allyn-stewart-tim-moore-producers-oscars-interview-1201871653/ |archivedate=2017-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。後來，他們去訪問蘇倫柏格，蘇倫柏格表示，「我不認為你們得照著書來拍電影」，並告訴了三人一個故事。之後，該故事便成為了電影的靈感來源<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。蘇倫柏格希望該片能圍繞著「人們共同的人性」，並指出該次事件是在2008年的[[經濟大衰退|經濟大衰退]]後發生的：「人們懷疑一切事物是否皆與自利及貪婪有關。他們質疑人的本性。然後眾人無私的互助合作，促成了一件非常重要的事情。我認為這給了大家懷有一絲希望的機會，在這個時候，我們所有人都需要它」<ref name="Varietyhumanity">{{cite web |last=Rainy |first=James |title=Tom Hanks, Chesley Sullenberger Hail 'Common Humanity' of Clint Eastwood's 'Sully' |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/tom-hanks-clint-eastwood-sully-1201847050/ |website=''Variety'' |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025071603/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/tom-hanks-clint-eastwood-sully-1201847050/ |archivedate=2017-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。製作人們聘請陶德·柯馬爾尼茲基（{{lang|en|Todd Komarnicki}}）來編寫劇本<ref name="screenplay"/>。柯馬爾尼茲基表示，編劇的困難之處不在於處理迫降在河上的橋段，因為大家早已知之甚詳，真正困難的是事後調查的部分<ref name="Creative Screenwriting">{{cite web |last=McKittrick |first=Christopher |title=The Eternal Now: Todd Komarnicki on Sully |url=http://creativescreenwriting.com/sully/ |website=''Creative Screenwriting'' |accessdate=2016-10-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809142406/https://creativescreenwriting.com/sully/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[克林·伊斯威特|克林·伊斯威特]]同時身兼導演及製片人，其他製片人包含法蘭克·馬歇爾、艾琳·史都華與提姆·摩爾（{{lang|en|Tim Moore}}），而史蒂夫·莫尼陳（{{lang|en|Steven Mnuchin}}）、奇普·尼爾森及{{link-en|布魯斯·貝爾曼|Bruce Berman}}則是該片的執行製片人<ref name="McCarthy">{{Cite news|last=McCarthy|first=Todd|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/tom-hanks-clint-eastwoods-sully-924501|title='Sully': Telluride Review|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|date=2016-09-09|accessdate=2016-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814103418/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/tom-hanks-clint-eastwoods-sully-924501|archivedate=2017-08-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>。該片的選角導演由傑佛瑞·米克拉特（{{lang|en|Geoffrey Miclat}}）擔任<ref name="McCarthy"/>。

2015年6月，據報導，[[湯姆·漢克斯|湯姆·漢克斯]]正為飾演蘇倫柏格一事與[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]進行討論<ref name="HanksCast">{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Tom Hanks In Talks To Play Heroic Pilot Sully Sullenberger In Clint Eastwood Film|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/tom-hanks-sully-sullenberger-clint-eastwood-movie-1201447178/|accessdate=2015-06-19|work=Deadline.com|date=2015-06-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314061659/http://deadline.com/2015/06/tom-hanks-sully-sullenberger-clint-eastwood-movie-1201447178/|archivedate=2017-03-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>。8月，[[亞倫·艾克哈特|亞倫·艾克哈特]]<ref name="EckhartCast">{{cite news|last1=Ford|first1=Rebecca|last2=McClintock|first2=Pamela|title=Aaron Eckhart Joins Tom Hanks in Captain Sully Movie (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/aaron-eckhart-joins-tom-hanks-814613|accessdate=2015-08-18|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|date=2015-08-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807153514/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/aaron-eckhart-joins-tom-hanks-814613|archivedate=2017-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>、[[蘿拉·琳妮|蘿拉·琳妮]]<ref name="LinneyCast"/>、[[赫特·麥卡藍|赫特·麥卡藍]]<ref name="McCallanyCast"/>與[[傑米·謝爾丹|傑米·謝爾丹]]<ref name="SheridanCast">{{cite news|last1=Ford|first1=Rebecca|title=Captain Sully Movie Adds Jamey Sheridan (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tom-hanks-capt-sully-movie-818208|accessdate=2015-11-09|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|date=2015-08-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807154051/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tom-hanks-capt-sully-movie-818208|archivedate=2017-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>加入劇組。{{link-en|傑瑞·費拉拉|Jerry Ferrara}}於9月簽約出演電影<ref name="FerraraCast"/>。《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》的[[主体拍摄|主體拍攝]]始於9月28日，地點位在美國[[紐約市|紐約市]]<ref name="Filming-1">{{cite news|last1=Lesnick|first1=Silas|title=Clint Eastwood and Tom Hanks Begin Production on Sully|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/618441-clint-eastwood-and-tom-hanks-begin-production-on-sully|accessdate=2015-10-02|work=Comingsoon.net|date=2015-09-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807153638/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/618441-clint-eastwood-and-tom-hanks-begin-production-on-sully|archivedate=2017-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>，由長期與伊斯威特合作的[[湯姆·史登|湯姆·史登]]<ref>{{Cite web|title='American Sniper' Cinematographer Tom Stern to Appear at NAB Show; Creative Master Series Keynote and Lineup Unveiled|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20150316005920/en/American-Sniper-Cinematographer-Tom-Stern-to-Appear-at-NAB-Show-Creative-Master-Series-Keynote-and-Lineup-Unveiled|accessdate=2021-01-10|author=|date=2015-03-16|format=|work=Business Wire|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513152828/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20150316005920/en/American-Sniper-Cinematographer-Tom-Stern-to-Appear-at-NAB-Show-Creative-Master-Series-Keynote-and-Lineup-Unveiled|dead-url=no}}</ref>掌鏡<ref name="THR (2016-09-09)"/>。該片的服裝設計師由{{link-en|黛博拉·霍柏|Deborah Hopper}}擔任，而道格·索爾曼（{{lang|en|Doug Coleman}}）則擔任該片的特技執導<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。10月，據報導，{{link-en|麥斯·阿德勒 (演員)|Max Adler (actor)|麥斯·阿德勒}}<ref name="AdlerCast"/>、[[山姆·杭汀頓|山姆·杭汀頓]]<ref name="HuntingtonCast"/>與{{link-en|韋恩·巴斯特厄普|Wayne Bastrup}}<ref name="BastrupCast"/>加入了主演的行列。10月15日，劇組在[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]取景，並將{{link-en|亞特蘭大市中心|Downtown Atlanta}}的一棟建築布置成紐約市的酒店進行拍攝<ref name="Filming-2">{{cite news|title=‘Sully’, starring Tom Hanks, moves from NYC to Atlanta|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/10/15/sully-starring-tom-hanks-moves-from-nyc-to-atlanta/|accessdate=2015-10-26|work=''On Location Vacations''|date=2015-10-15|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6vRCV56PQ?url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/10/15/sully-starring-tom-hanks-moves-from-nyc-to-atlanta/|archivedate=2017-12-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

該片大多數的預算都花在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，迫降及疏散的過程皆在那裡的華納兄弟工作室及環球影城攝製<ref name="Filming-3">{{Cite journal |date=2017-05 |title=2016 Feature Film Study |url=https://www.filmla.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2016_film_study_WEB.pdf |journal=FilmL.A. Feature Film Study |accessdate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731191957/https://www.filmla.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2016_film_study_WEB.pdf |archivedate=2017-07-31}}</ref>。劇組將一架[[空中巴士A320|空中巴士A320]]拆解，運到環球影城的瀑布湖（{{lang|en|Falls Lake}}）重新組裝，並替飛機裝設了350噸重的平衡環<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。平衡環裡有五個液壓滾輪，其中三個能讓飛機上下移動，另外兩個則能讓飛機左右搖晃<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。為了拍攝疏散乘客的場景，劇組架設了五台攝影機<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。劇組也拍了數個渡輪正面的鏡頭，好在後期製作中搭配使用<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。此外，劇組亦在[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]]、[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]的{{link-en|霍洛曼空軍基地|Holloman Air Force Base}}及[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]的{{link-en|卡尼 (紐澤西州)|Kearny, New Jersey|卡尼}}取景。劇組在紐約市拍攝了所有的廣角鏡頭，並在後期製作中透過特效將飛機加入片中<ref name="DVD (Neck Deep in the Hudson: Shooting Sully)"/>。拍攝作業於2015年11月25日結束<ref>{{Cite tweet |author= |author-link= |user=tomhanks |number=669349848592883712 |date=2015-11-25 |title=Warner Bros studios. Final day of shooting #SULLY.  Work done. Gloves off. Hanx. |script-title= |trans-title= |retweet= |access-date=2021-11-28 |archivedurl= |archivedate= |language= }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Tom Hanks claims he put £100 bet on Leicester to win the Premier League |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/04/26/tom-hanks-claims-he-bet-on-leicester-to-win-the-premier-league/ |access-date=2021-11-28 |date=2016-04-26 |work=The Telegraph |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128114952/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/04/26/tom-hanks-claims-he-bet-on-leicester-to-win-the-premier-league/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。就上映時間來看，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》是第一部幾乎全片都用[[阿萊Alexa|Alexa IMAX]]65數位攝影機拍攝的電影<ref name="THR (2016-09-09)"/><ref name="Filming-4">{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|title=Clint Eastwood Shooting ‘Sully’ Almost Entirely With Imax Cameras|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/clint-eastwood-sully-imax-1201758250/|work=''Variety''|date=2016-04-21|accessdate=2017-08-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807192223/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/clint-eastwood-sully-imax-1201758250/|archivedate=2017-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。電影的剪輯由布魯·穆雷（{{lang|en|Blu Murray}}）負責，此前他有11年在伊斯威特的作品中擔任助理，此次伊斯威特給了他首次擔當該職的機會<ref>{{Cite web |title=‘Sully’ Editor Cuts First Feature Alongside Clint Eastwood |url=https://variety.com/2016/artisans/production/sully-editor-blu-murray-1201865944/ |access-date=2021-11-28 |date=2016-09-21 |last=James |first=Daron |work=Variety |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128114917/https://variety.com/2016/artisans/production/sully-editor-blu-murray-1201865944/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

