== 上映與市場營銷 ==

[[File:Sully_Japan_Premiere_Red_Carpet-_Tom_Hanks_&_Aaron_Eckhart_(29830287495).jpg|thumb]]，[[艾伦·艾克哈特|亞倫·艾克哈特]]與[[汤姆·汉克斯|湯姆·漢克斯]]出席日本地區的首映禮]]

《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》於2016年9月2日在第43屆{{link-en|特柳賴德影展|Telluride Film Festival}}上首映，並於9月9日在美國上映（含[[IMAX|IMAX]]版本），發行商為[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]<ref name="release-1">{{cite news|last1=Stone|first1=Natalie|title=Clint Eastwood's 'Sully' Gets Early Fall Release Date|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/clint-eastwoods-sully-gets-early-850327|accessdate=2015-12-25|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|date=2015-12-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807154645/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/clint-eastwoods-sully-gets-early-850327|archivedate=2017-08-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。在決定將該片排定於2016年上映時，華納兄弟的高層考慮到許多給大人看的劇情片都在9月或10月下旬才上映，便打算把電影排在[[勞動節_(美國)|勞動節]]的週末上映<ref name="Sep11">{{cite web |last1=McClintock |first1=Pamela |date=2016-09-14 |title=Why 'Sully' Chose to Land Its Release Date Near 9/11 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/why-sully-chose-land-release-928562 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808090132/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/why-sully-chose-land-release-928562 |archivedate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。這表示該片的發行日期將與[[九一一襲擊事件|911襲擊事件]]的15週年紀念撞期，華納兄弟的高層對此感到相當憂心，因爲片中包含飛機撞上摩天大樓的場景（與911襲擊事件相似）。儘管如此，華納兄弟國內營銷部門的主管傑夫·戈德茨坦（{{lang|en|Jeff Goldstein}}）和他的團隊仍決定在該檔期上映，因為「《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》講述了一個希望的故事，以及一位盡忠職守的真英雄」<ref name="Sep11"/>。不過據編劇陶德·柯馬爾尼茲基的說法，該片的發行日期是巧合而非刻意。他表示，華納兄弟之所以會將該片排在這個檔期上映是因為IMAX劇院有限：在夏季，這些IMAX劇院通常都會被強檔電影包走；而在聖誕節期間，IMAX劇院又會被《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》電影給佔走<ref name="release-2">{{cite web |last1=Lee |first1=Ashley |date=2016-09-04 |title=Sully' Premiere: Clint Eastwood Defends Scenes of Planes Crashing Into Manhattan Skyscrapers |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/sully-premiere-clint-eastwood-defends-926117 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121071757/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/sully-premiere-clint-eastwood-defends-926117 |archivedate=2017-11-21 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

電影的首支預告片於2016年6月29日釋出<ref name="trailer-1">{{cite web |last1=Konerman |first1=Jennifer |date=2016-06-29 |title=Tom Hanks Suffers Through Hero Worship in 'Sully' Trailer |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tom-hanks-suffers-hero-worship-907506 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2017-08-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808160629/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tom-hanks-suffers-hero-worship-907506 |archivedate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="trailer-2">{{cite news|title=Watch the First ‘Sully’ Trailer: Tom Hanks Stars as Hero Pilot|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/sully-trailer-tom-hanks-video-pilot-1201806340/|accessdate=2016-06-29|work=''Variety''|date=2017-08-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808154029/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/sully-trailer-tom-hanks-video-pilot-1201806340/|archivedate=2017-08-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>。IMAX版本的預告於8月19日發布<ref name="trailer-IMAX">{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Sully IMAX Trailer Features Tom Hanks & Clint Eastwood|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/trailers/759461-sully-imax-trailer-features-tom-hanks-clint-eastwood#/slide/1|accessdate=2017-08-08|work=Comingsoon.net|date=2016-08-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808155253/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/trailers/759461-sully-imax-trailer-features-tom-hanks-clint-eastwood|archivedate=2017-08-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]（MPAA）以片中有「一些驚險場面及髒話」為由將電影評為[[美国电影分级制度#美國電影協會電影分級|PG-13級]]，意味著片中含有部分家長可能認為不適合13歲以下觀眾觀看的內容，建議家長需特別注意<ref name="RT">{{cite web |title=Sully (2016) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sully |website=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Fandango |accessdate=2017-06-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126151825/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sully |archivedate=2017-11-26 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==

=== 評價 ===

《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》收穫了多數影評人的正面評價。影評匯總網站[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的346篇專業影評文章中，有293篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為85%，平均得分7.2分（滿分10分），該網站對電影的共識性評價寫道「正如同片中鼓舞人心、技藝精湛的主人翁，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》善用了來自其主演及導演的高超表現，來對日常生活中的英雄致上一些無聲的敬意」<ref name="RT"/>，而[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則根據46篇評論文章，其中35篇予以好評，無差評，11篇褒貶不一，給出平均分74（滿分100），綜合結果為「普遍良好的評價」<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web |title=Sully Reviews |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/sully |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2016-09-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002090948/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/sully |archivedate=2017-10-02 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。據[[影院評分|CinemaScore]]進行的調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |author=CinemaScore on Twitter |date=2016-09-10 |title=Sully |url=https://mobile.twitter.com/cinemascore/status/774480878055456768 |work=Twitter |accessdate=2017-04-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519195457/https://mobile.twitter.com/CinemaScore/status/774480878055456768 |archivedate=2017-05-19}}</ref>。[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]（AFI）將該片排在年度十大電影名單中的第九名<ref name="AFI">{{cite web |last=Hipes |first=Patrick |date=2016-12-08 |title=AFI Awards: Best Of 2016 List Includes 'Silence', 'Hacksaw Ridge' & More |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/afi-awards-film-2016-list-silence-sully-zootopia-1201867080/ |publisher=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-12-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222192150/http://deadline.com/2016/12/afi-awards-film-2016-list-silence-sully-zootopia-1201867080/ |archivedate=2017-01-16 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌的彼得·迪布吉（{{lang|en|Peter Debruge}}）給予該片好評，並稱讚了[[湯姆·漢克斯|湯姆·漢克斯]]的表現，「漢克斯的表現既經典又強大，很快的，我們便忘了自己正看著一名演員」<ref name="Debruge">{{cite web |last1=Debruge |first1=Peter |date=2016-09-02 |title=Telluride Film Review: ‘Sully’ |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/sully-review-1201848771/ |work=''Variety'' |accessdate=2017-08-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204235419/http://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/sully-review-1201848771/ |archivedate=2017-12-04 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的影評人賽門·-{zh-hant:湯;zh-hans:汤;}-普森（{{lang|en|Simon Thompson}}）給予該片9分（滿分10分）的評價，稱《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》是一部「美麗且和諧，卓越又細膩的感人電影」，並稱該片是「湯姆·漢克斯從影以來的最佳演出」。同時，湯普森也指出導演[[克林·伊斯威特|克林·伊斯威特]]的手法「美妙又濃厚」<ref name="Thompson">{{cite web |last1=Thompson |first1=Simon |date=2016-09-08 |title=Sully Review |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/09/08/sully-review |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128125311/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/09/08/sully-review |archivedate=2017-11-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{link-en|曼諾拉·吉斯|Manohla Dargis}}亦稱讚了伊斯威特的導演功力，表示該片「不會讓你失望」<ref name="Dargis">{{Cite news|last1=Dargis|first1=Manohla|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/09/movies/sully-review.html?_r=0|title=Review: Sully Landed the Plane. Then He Had to Endure the Spotlight.|newspaper=''The New York Times''|date=2016-09-08|accessdate=2016-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812063411/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/09/movies/sully-review.html?_r=0|archivedate=2017-08-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》的影評人[[陶德·麥卡錫|陶德·麥卡錫]]稱該片為一部「優雅且具說服力的紀錄片」<ref name="McCarthy"/>。《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》雜誌的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]給出了3.5顆星（滿分4顆）的分數，寫道「該片透過深入發掘贏得你的目光及尊敬」，並稱《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》「讓人眼界大開」<ref name="Travers">{{Cite web |last1=Travers |first1=Peter |date=2016-09-08 |title='Sully' Review: Clint Eastwood, Tom Hanks Make Heroic Pilot Story Soar |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/peter-travers-sully-movie-review-w438062 |work=''Rolling Stone'' |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128102024/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/peter-travers-sully-movie-review-w438062 |archivedate=2017-11-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的{{link-en|理察·羅珀|Richard Roeper}}給出了4顆星的滿分好評，稱該片為「令人振奮的驚悚片」，並讚譽漢克斯的表現「令人難忘」。此外，羅珀亦稱讚了電影的剪輯與視覺效果<ref name="Roeper">{{Cite web |last1=Roeper |first1=Richard |date=2016-09-06 |title='Sully': Brace for emotional impact of Tom Hanks' cockpit triumph |url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/sully-brace-for-emotional-impact-of-tom-hanks-cockpit-triumph/ |work=''Chicago Sun-Times'' |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129020048/http://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/sully-brace-for-emotional-impact-of-tom-hanks-cockpit-triumph/ |archivedate=2017-11-29 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

相反的，《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》的約翰·安德森（{{lang|en|John Anderson}}）給出了負面評論，表示該片有些沉悶<ref name="Anderson">{{cite news|last1=Anderson|first1=John|url=http://time.com/4482436/sully-movie-review-tom-hanks/|title=Review: Clint Eastwood’s Dutiful Sully Is Too Heavy for Liftoff|work=''[[時代雜誌|Time]]''|date=2016-09-07|accessdate=2017-08-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201124602/http://time.com/4482436/sully-movie-review-tom-hanks/|archivedate=2017-12-01|deadurl=no}}</ref>。此外，他亦寫道，儘管與[[全美航空1549號班機事故|全美航空1549號班機事故]]相隔8年，但[[九一一襲擊事件|911襲擊事件]]仍在電影中縈繞不去：掠過紐澤西州的天際線的飛機，讓人聯想到大樓倒塌的那一天。安德森表示，從這一切可以看出電影對恐怖攻擊的隱喻以及導演對美國前景走向的不滿<ref name="Anderson"/>。《{{link-en|芝加哥讀者報|Chicago Reader}}》的J·R·瓊斯（{{lang|en|J. R. Jones}}）給出1顆星（滿分4顆）的負評，寫道「正如克林·伊斯威特的《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》呈現出來的那樣，哈德遜奇蹟其實不是一個拍電影的好題材」<ref name="Jones">{{cite web |last1=Jones |first1=J. R. |date=2016-09-15 |title=With Sully, Clint Eastwood recalls a story no one has forgotten yet |url=https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/sully-clint-eastwood-chesley-sullenberger-tom-hanks/Content?oid=23488556 |work=''Chicago Reader'' |accessdate=2017-08-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128015107/https://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/sully-clint-eastwood-chesley-sullenberger-tom-hanks/Content?oid=23488556 |archivedate=2017-11-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《{{link-en|底特律新聞報|The Detroit News}}》的亞當·古溫漢（{{lang|en|Adam Graham}}）給出「C+」的評分，表示「從這部電影可以看出，伊斯威特急著了事去拍別部片」<ref name="Graham">{{cite web |last1=Graham |first1=Adam |date=2016-09-09 |title=Review: Hanks solid, but ‘Sully’ otherwise falters |url=http://www.detroitnews.com/story/entertainment/movies/2016/09/08/movie-review-hanks-solid-sully-otherwise-falters/90104740/ |work=''The Detroit News'' |accessdate=2017-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128064304/http://www.detroitnews.com/story/entertainment/movies/2016/09/08/movie-review-hanks-solid-sully-otherwise-falters/90104740/ |archivedate=2017-11-28 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===

截至下檔日，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》在美國及加拿大地區共-{zh-hant:累積;zh-hans:累积;}-了1.25億美元的票房，加上來自其他地區的1.15億美元，全球票房共計2.4億美元，而其製片預算則是6,000萬美元<ref name="BOM">{{cite web |title=Sully (2016) |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=sully.htm |website=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-12-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703134259/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=sully.htm |archivedate=2017-07-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。IMAX方面，該片在首映當天透過全球各地的523家IMAX放映廳收穫510萬美元的票房，打破2D電影的9月IMAX開畫票房紀錄，原保持者為2014年的《[[移動迷宮_(電影)|移動迷宮]]》（420萬美元）<ref name="Overseas39thOpening">{{cite web |last1=Busch |first1=Anita |date=2016-09-13 |title=‘Sully’ Flies Higher In Offshore Debut; ‘Suicide Squad’ Squashes $700M WW – International Box Office Final |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-mil-jeong-suicide-squad-international-box-office-1201817102/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808153609/http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-mil-jeong-suicide-squad-international-box-office-1201817102/ |archivedate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。最終，電影在IMAX方面進帳了1,000萬美元的票房<ref name="Overseas40thOpening">{{cite web |last1=Tartaglione |first1=Nancy |date=2016-09-18 |title=‘Bridget Jones’s Baby’ Bows To $30M; ‘Suicide Squad’ Powers Past $400M – Intl Box Office |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/bridget-jones-baby-suicide-squad-chinese-odyssey-sully-overseas-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201821739/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905033622/http://deadline.com/2016/09/bridget-jones-baby-suicide-squad-chinese-odyssey-sully-overseas-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201821739/ |archivedate=2017-09-05 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

==== 美國與加拿大 ====

[[File:ClintEastwoodCannesMay08.jpg|thumb]]的職業生涯中，北美地區首映當天票房第二高的電影，僅次於《[[美國狙擊手_(電影)|美國狙擊手]]》（2014年）]]

在美國及加拿大，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》與同期上映的《{{link-en|鬼開門|The Disappointments Room}}》、《{{link-en|驚魂契約|When the Bough Breaks (2016 film)}}》及《{{link-en|魯濱遜漂流記 (2016年電影)|Robinson Crusoe (2016 film)|魯濱遜漂流記}}》共同競爭，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》及《綜藝》雜誌推測該片能在首週末透過3,525家電影院（其中375家能放映IMAX版本）進帳2,500萬美元，而[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]則預計該片將在首週末收穫3,100萬美元<ref name="LAT (2016-09-06)">{{cite web |last1=Faughnder |first1=Ryan |date=2016-09-06 |title='Sully' and 'When the Bough Breaks' to choke 'Don't Breathe' at the box office |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20160906-snap-story.html |work=''Los Angeles Times'' |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807152747/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20160906-snap-story.html |archivedate=2017-08-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Preview-1">{{cite web |last1=McClintock |first1=Pamela |date=2016-09-09 |title=Box-Office Preview: 'Sully' Buckles Up for Strong Takeoff as Fall Commences |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-sully-bough-breaks-926496 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807153126/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-sully-bough-breaks-926496 |archivedate=2017-08-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Preview-2">{{cite web |last1=McNary |first1=Dave |date=2016-09-06 |title=Box Office: Tom Hanks’ Sully’ Set to Land With Moderate $25 Million |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/sully-box-office-tom-hanks-when-the-bough-breaks-1201853135/ |work=''Variety'' |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807192410/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/sully-box-office-tom-hanks-when-the-bough-breaks-1201853135/ |archivedate=2017-08-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Preview-3">{{cite web |last1=Brevet |first1=Brad |date=2016-09-08 |title='Sully' and 'When the Bough Breaks' Set to Kick Off Fall 2016 Movie Season |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4198 |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808193136/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4198 |archivedate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。外界預估，該片的開畫成績可能會與湯姆·漢克斯的另一部作品《[[怒海劫|怒海劫]]》（2013年，2,570萬美元）及同樣與航空事故有關的電影《[[機密真相|機密真相]]》（2012年，2,490年）相去不遠。《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》於美國的[[勞動節_(美國)|勞動節]]週末上映，根據既往的經驗，在勞動節上映的電影票房往往不盡理想；但[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]指出，這個公式並不適合套用在每部電影，其票房成績取決於該電影的類型<ref name="DDD">{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |date=2016-09-07 |title=Clint Eastwood’s ‘Sully’ Launches Fall Awards Season, But Can ‘Bough’ Break At No. 1? – B.O. Preview |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-when-the-bough-breaks-disappointments-room-1201814430/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807153923/http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-when-the-bough-breaks-disappointments-room-1201814430/ |archivedate=2017-08-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。據售票網站[[Fandango_Media|Fandango Media]]的資料顯示，電影的門票預售量超越了漢克斯的另一部作品《[[間諜橋|間諜橋]]》（2015年）的預售量<ref name="DDD"/>。該片在星期四的午夜場透過2,700家電影院收穫135萬美元，為漢克斯職業生涯中最佳的成績<ref name="Thursday">{{cite web |last1=Busch |first1=Anita |date=2016-09-09 |title=‘Sully’ Soars With $1.35M For Warner Bros. — Thursday Box Office |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025080331/http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |archivedate=2017-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>；Box Office Mojo認為這是一個相當強勁的表現，考量到該片的午夜場正好與{{link-en|2016年NFL賽季|2016 NFL season}}的第一場比賽撞期<ref name="Preview-3"/>。

首映當天，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》進帳了1,220萬美元（包含星期四的午夜場的收入）的票房，其中130萬美元來自IMAX版本<ref name="Dead">{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |date=2016-09-11 |title='Sully' Soaring, ‘Bough’ Breaks To Mid-Teen, ‘Wild Life’ Snoozing, ‘Disappointments’ DOA |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025080331/http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |archivedate=2017-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。該片為導演克林·伊斯威特生涯中首映當天票房第二高的電影，僅次於《[[美國狙擊手_(電影)|美國狙擊手]]》（2014年，3,000萬美元）<ref name="Forbes (2016-09-10)">{{cite web |last1=Mendelson |first1=Scott |date=2016-09-10 |title=Friday Box Office: Tom Hanks And Clint Eastwood's 'Sully' Soars To $12.2 Million |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/09/10/friday-box-office-tom-hanks-and-clint-eastwoods-sully-soars-to-12-2-million/#79bd455816a8 |work=''Forbes'' |accessdate=2016-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809002339/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/09/10/friday-box-office-tom-hanks-and-clint-eastwoods-sully-soars-to-12-2-million/#4f3e406910a5 |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。截止至首週末，電影已累積了3,500萬美元的票房，位居當週票房冠軍，並名列史上於9月上映的電影票房的前五名（若考慮到通貨膨脹的話則為第12名）<ref name="Weekend-1">{{cite web |last1=McClintock |first1=Pamela |date=2016-09-11 |title=Weekend Box Office: Tom Hanks' 'Sully' Flies to Stellar $35.5M Debut |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-sully-flies-92743 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2016-09-11}}</ref><ref name="Weekend-2">{{cite web |title=TOP OPENING WEEKENDS BY MONTH |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=09&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807192246/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=09&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm |archivedate=2017-08-07 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。該成績僅次於伊斯威特的《美國狙擊手》（8,900萬美元），位列伊斯威特的作品中第二佳的首週末票房成績。同時，該片也是漢克斯的真人作品中第三高的首週末票房成績，次於《[[達文西密碼_(電影)|達文西密碼]]》（2006年，7,700萬美元）與《[[天使與魔鬼_(電影)|天使與魔鬼]]》（2009年，4,600萬美元）之後<ref name="Weekend-3">{{cite web |last1=Mendelson |first1=Scott |date=2016-09-11 |title=Box Office: 'Sully' Soars With $35.5 Million Debut Weekend |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/09/11/box-office-sully-soars-with-35-5-million-debut-weekend/#1ca67d74df7b |work=''Forbes'' |accessdate=2016-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808004203/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/09/11/box-office-sully-soars-with-35-5-million-debut-weekend/#70fc8ccf2f99 |archivedate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。電影在IMAX方面的票房表現也非常出色，僅在首週末就破紀錄地在375家IMAX放映廳上映，進帳了400萬美元，佔該週票房收入的11%。該成績打破了《[[私刑教育|私刑教育]]》（2014年，310萬美元）在2014年9月創下的紀錄<ref name="DEAD1">{{cite web |last1=Busch |first1=Anita |last2=D'Alessandro |first2=Anthony |date=2016-09-11 |title=‘Sully’ Soars To $35.5M For Biggest Post-Labor Day Weekend, ‘Bough’ Breaks With $15M – Sunday Update |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025080331/http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |archivedate=2017-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]與[[威秀電影|威秀電影]]對該片的票房表現興奮不已，電影院老闆亦是如此，因9月份正逢開學的時候，且電視台開始播出新節目，往往會使電影的票房下跌<ref name="The New York Times (2016-09-11)">{{cite web |last1=Barnes |first1=Brooks |date=2016-09-11 |title=‘Sully’ Flies High and Lands Smoothly at the Box Office |url=http://mobile.nytimes.com/2016/09/12/movies/sully-flies-high-and-lands-smoothly-at-the-box-office.html?rref=collection%2Fsectioncollection%2Fmovies&action=click&contentCollection=movies&region=rank&module=package&version=highlights&contentPlacement=7&pgtype=sectionfront&referer=https://www.nytimes.com/section/movies |work=''The New York Times'' |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809091327/https://mobile.nytimes.com/2016/09/12/movies/sully-flies-high-and-lands-smoothly-at-the-box-office.html?rref=collection%2Fsectioncollection%2Fmovies&action=click&contentCollection=movies&region=rank&module=package&version=highlights&contentPlacement=7&pgtype=sectionfront&referer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fsection%2Fmovies |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《[[富比士|富比士]]》雜誌的史考特·曼德森（{{lang|en|Scott Mendelson}}）預測，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》的票房有望達到1億美元，因為湯姆·漢克斯的作品往往都能「撐很久」，且該片的題材針對了那些平常都不會在首映週末去看電影的年長觀眾<ref name="Weekend-3"/>。Deadline.com指出，市場營銷是開畫成績的關鍵，儘管伊斯威特和漢克斯都沒有在社交媒體上露面，但其良好的口碑及影評人的積極評價亦助長了票房成績<ref name="Deadline.com (2016-09-12)">{{cite web |last1=Busch |first1=Anita |last2=D'Alessandro |first2=Anthony |date=2016-09-12 |title=‘Sully’ Lands At $35M, ‘Bough’ Breaks With $14.2M – Monday B.O. Final |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025080331/http://deadline.com/2016/09/sully-glides-in-with-1-35m-for-warner-bros-thursday-box-office-1201815274/ |archivedate=2017-10-25 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。電影在[[九一一襲擊事件|911襲擊事件]]的15週年紀念日首映，但華納兄弟國內營銷部門的主管傑夫·戈爾茨坦表示，這並未對電影產生重大的負面影響。據CinemaScore進行的調查，首映週末的觀眾中25歲以上的佔82%，35歲以上的佔80%，女性佔56%。39%的觀眾表示，漢克斯是他們進劇院看電影的主要原因<ref name="USA Today (2016-09-12)">{{cite web |last1=Truitt |first1=Brian |date=2016-09-12 |title=Tom Hanks' 'Sully' soars at box office with $35.5M |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/09/11/box-office-tom-hanks-sully-when-the-bough-breaks/90011704/ |work=''USA Today'' |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809175919/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/09/11/box-office-tom-hanks-sully-when-the-bough-breaks/90011704/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Moviefone (2016-09-12)">{{cite web |last1=Susman |first1=Gary |date=2016-09-12 |title=7 Reasons Why 'Sully' Shattered Expectations at the Box Office |url=http://www.moviefone.com/2016/09/12/sully-box-office-tom-hanks-clint-eastwood/ |work=Moviefone |accessdate=2016-09-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809131254/https://www.moviefone.com/2016/09/12/sully-box-office-tom-hanks-clint-eastwood/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

隔週，儘管該片面臨與新片《{{link-en|追殺厄夜叢林|Blair Witch (film)}}》、《[[BJ有喜|BJ有喜]]》及《[[神鬼駭客：史諾登|神鬼駭客：史諾登]]》的激烈競爭，票房成績僅下跌了36%，最終仍收穫了2,160萬美元，蟬聯冠軍寶座<ref name="second weekend">{{cite web |last1=McClintock |first1=Pamela |date=2016-09-18 |title=Weekend Box Office: 'Bridget Jones's Baby' Bombs in U.S. With $8M; 'Sully' Stays No. 1 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-bridget-joness-929980 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2016-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809093346/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-bridget-jones-bombs-sully-snowden-929980 |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。第三週，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》收穫了1,550萬美元，被新上映的《[[絕地7騎士|絕地7騎士]]》（3,470萬美元）及《[[送子鳥_(電影)|送子鳥]]》（2,130萬美元）擠下，位居第三<ref name="third weekend">{{cite web |last1=D'Alessandro |first1=Anthony |date=2016-09-26 |title=‘Magnificent Seven’ Lassos $59.3M Worldwide & Record $34.7M U.S. Opening For Antoine Fuqua – Monday Final B.O. |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/magnificent-seven-storks-sully-weekend-box-office-1201824971/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809041509/http://deadline.com/2016/09/magnificent-seven-storks-sully-weekend-box-office-1201824971/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。到了第四週，該片進帳830萬美元，排名當週第五，總票房突破1億美元大關<ref name="THR (2016-10-02)">{{cite web |last1=McClintock |first1=Pamela |date=2016-10-02 |title=Weekend Box Office: 'Miss Peregrine's' Blows Past 'Deepwater Horizon' With $28.5M |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-miss-peregrine-934482 |work=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2016-10-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6xJcwJPWy?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-miss-peregrine-934482 |archivedate=2018-02-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

