==== 其他地區 ====

該片同時也在全球的其他39個國家上映，從世界各地約3,600家電影院收穫了約1,050萬美元的票房<ref name="DEAD1"/>。在IMAX版本方面，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》透過全球各地的148家IMAX電影院中進帳了110萬美元的票房<ref name="Overseas39thOpening"/>。電影於俄羅斯的首週末票房為100萬美元，僅次於《[[賓漢_(2016年電影)|賓漢]]》及《[[腸腸搞轟趴|腸腸搞轟趴]]》，位居當週第三。該成績也使該片成為伊斯威特在俄羅斯首周末票房最高的作品。電影在[[阿拉伯聯合大公國|阿拉伯聯合大公國]]進帳了100萬美元的票房。該片在澳大利亞上映的檔期適逢澳大利亞的[[父親節|父親節]]，共收穫240萬美元的票房<ref name="Overseas39thOpening"/>。《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》在[[中秋節|中秋節]]期間於香港上映，票房收入為77.7萬美元<ref name="Overseas40thOpening"/>。該片在日本收穫240萬美元，成為伊斯威特在日本第三賣座的電影，次於《美國狙擊手》及《[[來自硫磺島的信|來自硫磺島的信]]》（2006年）<ref name="Overseas41stOpening">{{cite web |last1=Tartaglione |first1=Nancy |date=2016-09-25 |title=‘Bridget Jones’s Baby’ Tops Overseas Again As ‘Magnificent 7’ Corrals $19.2M & ‘Storks’ Bundles $18.3M – Intl Box Office |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/storks-magnificent-seven-bridget-jones-baby-finding-dory-overseas-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201825820/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-09-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809040914/http://deadline.com/2016/09/storks-magnificent-seven-bridget-jones-baby-finding-dory-overseas-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201825820/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。該片在日本的總票房為1,320萬美元<ref name="HOLL2">{{cite web |last1=Tartaglione |first1=Nancy |date=2016-12-11 |title=‘Fantastic Beasts’ Conjures $680M WW; ‘Christmas Party’ & ‘Sing’ Swing; ‘Hacksaw’ Wows In China Bow – Intl Box Office |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/fantastic-beasts-office-christmas-party-sing-moana-hacksaw-ridge-la-la-land-overseas-china-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201868226/ |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809130353/http://deadline.com/2016/12/fantastic-beasts-office-christmas-party-sing-moana-hacksaw-ridge-la-la-land-overseas-china-weekend-results-international-box-office-1201868226/ |archivedate=2017-08-09 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="International Box Office Results">{{cite web |title=Sully International Box Office Results |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=sully.htm |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108044712/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=sully.htm |archivedate=2017-11-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。在巴西發生[[拉米亞航空2933號班機空難|拉米亞航空2933號班機空難]]後，華納兄弟宣布將巴西的上映日期從12月1日<ref name="Brazil-1">{{Cite news|url=http://g1.globo.com/pop-arte/cinema/noticia/2016/11/sully-tem-estreia-adiada-no-brasil-apos-queda-de-aviao.html|title='Sully' tem estreia adiada no Brasil após queda de avião da Chapecoense|date=2016-11-29|newspaper=Cinema|accessdate=2016-12-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809090540/http://g1.globo.com/pop-arte/cinema/noticia/2016/11/sully-tem-estreia-adiada-no-brasil-apos-queda-de-aviao.html|archivedate=2017-08-09|deadurl=no}}</ref>延至12月15日<ref name="Brazil-2">{{Cite news|url=http://zh.clicrbs.com.br/rs/entretenimento/cinema/noticia/2016/12/sully-adiado-apos-acidente-com-chapecoense-filme-sobre-pouso-forcado-tem-nova-data-de-estreia-8626273.html|title="Sully": adiado após acidente com Chapecoense, filme sobre pouso forçado tem nova data de estreia|newspaper=ZH 2014|accessdate=2016-12-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809130440/http://zh.clicrbs.com.br/rs/entretenimento/cinema/noticia/2016/12/sully-adiado-apos-acidente-com-chapecoense-filme-sobre-pouso-forcado-tem-nova-data-de-estreia-8626273.html|archivedate=2017-08-09|deadurl=no}}</ref>。截至2017年1月，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》已在巴西收穫了189萬美元的票房<ref name="BOM-Foreign">{{cite web |title=Sully-Foreign |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=sully.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2017-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108044712/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=sully.htm |archivedate=2017-11-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

中國大陸方面，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》在一個競爭激烈的檔期（2016年12月9日）上映<ref name="HOLL2"/>。該片於首映週末透過約5,000個大螢幕進帳550萬美元<ref name="HOLL2"/>，最終累積票房約為6,230萬人民幣<ref name="藝恩電影營銷智庫">{{cite web |title=萨利机长（2016） |url=http://www.cbooo.cn/m/656002 |work=藝恩電影營銷智庫 |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2017-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918202335/http://www.cbooo.cn/m/656002 |archivedate=2017-09-18 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

