== 家庭媒體 ==

《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》的數位HD版本於2016年12月9日由{{link-en|華納家庭娛樂|Warner Home Video}}發行，而[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]及[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]則於12月20日推出<ref name="Home media">{{cite web |title=Sully (2016) |url=http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/7801/sully |work=DVDsReleaseDates.com |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808154119/http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/7801/sully |archivedate=2017-08-08 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。在美國，《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》的DVD於發行首週賣出約43萬份，而藍光光碟則賣出約30萬份。截至2020年7月，該片已在家庭媒體方面收穫了約2,818萬美元的收益<ref name="The Numbers DVD/BD">{{cite web |title=Sully (2016) Video sales |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Sully#tab=video-sales |publisher=The Numbers |accessdate=2017-09-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917213609/http://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Sully#tab=summary |archivedate=2017-09-17 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 爭議與歷史偏差 ==

[[File:Christine_Negroni_headshot.jpg|thumb]]

《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》對[[國家運輸安全委員會|國家運輸安全委員會]]（NTSB）的描述引發了爭議。在電影上映後，NTSB的人員表示，他們不滿片中對他們的描寫<ref name="WP Review">{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/hanks-eckhart-take-flight-as-real-life-heroes-in-sully/2016/09/07/c7cf3832-752d-11e6-9781-49e591781754_story.html|title=Hanks, Eckhart take flight as real-life heroes in ‘Sully’|last1=Bahr|first1=Lindsey|newspaper=''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]''|date=2016-09-07|accessdate=2017-08-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919135300/https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/hanks-eckhart-take-flight-as-real-life-heroes-in-sully/2016/09/07/c7cf3832-752d-11e6-9781-49e591781754_story.html|archivedate=2016-09-19|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="Bustle (2016-09-09)">{{cite web |last1=Truffaut-Wong |first1=Olivia |date=2016-09-09 |title=How Accurate Is 'Sully'? The New Movie Sticks Close To The Captain's Story |url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/182938-how-accurate-is-sully-the-new-movie-sticks-close-to-the-captains-story |work=''Bustle'' |accessdate=2017-08-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814175755/https://www.bustle.com/articles/182938-how-accurate-is-sully-the-new-movie-sticks-close-to-the-captains-story |archivedate=2017-08-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|克莉絲汀·納格羅尼|Christine Negroni}}在《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》上寫道，「電影對調查的描述偏離了官方的紀錄」，並指稱該片描述調查人員「違反航空事故調查的協定」且「不知變通」<ref name="NYT Off-Screen Drama">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/10/business/sully-is-latest-historical-film-to-prompt-off-screen-drama.html|title=‘Sully’ Is Latest Historical Film to Prompt Off-Screen Drama|last=Negroni|first=Christine|date=2016-09-09|newspaper=''The New York Times''|accessdate=2016-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171123013239/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/10/business/sully-is-latest-historical-film-to-prompt-off-screen-drama.html|archivedate=2017-11-23|deadurl=no}}</ref>。NTSB的調查人員約翰·巴爾札諾（{{lang|en|John Balzano}}）對此描述表達不滿，稱調查人員「根本沒有為難任何人」。前NTSB調查人員表示，他擔心觀眾會將其視為「政府無能」的證據<ref name="AP Investigators Object">{{cite news|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/8def306d398340fd8a80d232c96e43b7/real-life-investigators-object-portrayal-sully-movie|title=Real-life investigators object to portrayal in 'Sully' movie|last=Lowy|first=Joan|work=Associated Press|date=2016-09-08|accessdate=2016-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215181427/https://apnews.com/8def306d398340fd8a80d232c96e43b7/real-life-investigators-object-portrayal-sully-movie|archivedate=2017-12-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。雖然在電影中，模擬器顯示，飛機應該在機場降落；但在實際的公開聽證會上，NTSB的調查人員勞勃·班森（{{lang|en|Robert Benzon}}）表示，「這些模擬器顯示，飛返[[拉瓜地亞機場|拉瓜地亞機場]]降落或飛往{{link-en|泰特伯勒機場|Teterboro Airport}}降落是相當冒險的決定」<ref name="NTSB public hearing">{{cite web |date=2009-06-09 |title=Transcript - Public Hearing Day 1 |url=http://www.exosphere3d.com/pubwww/pdf/flight_1549/ntsb_docket/422295.pdf |page=page 18, lines 23–25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091222015803/http://www.exosphere3d.com/pubwww/pdf/flight_1549/ntsb_docket/422295.pdf |archivedate=2009-12-22 |accessdate=2017-01-05 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。該片上映後，班森說：「我不知道為什麼編劇和導演選擇把NTSB的人員扭曲成這個與事實不同的樣子」，認為該片「可能不利於航空安全」<ref name="The Daily Beast (2016-09-18)">{{cite web |last1=Irving |first1=Clive |date=2016-09-18 |title=The Unsung Hero Left Out of ‘Sully’ |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/09/18/the-unsung-hero-left-out-of-sully.html |work=''The Daily Beast'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504120036/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/09/18/the-unsung-hero-left-out-of-sully.html |archivedate=2017-05-04 |accessdate=2017-05-04 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。華納兄弟對此發表了評論，但未得到回覆<ref name="Bustle (2016-09-09)"/>。

[[湯姆·漢克斯|湯姆·漢克斯]]告訴[[美聯社|美聯社]]，蘇倫柏格在看過了劇本初稿後，要求修改劇本，移除當中NTSB调查人员的真实姓名。據漢克的說法，蘇倫柏格認為現實生活中的調查人員「不是檢察官」，而將他們扯進這個將NTSB調查寫得「更像控告程序」的故事中是不公平的<ref name="AP Investigators Object"/>。全美航空1549號班機的駕駛艙錄音顯示，蘇倫柏格在起飛前用手機打了一通短暫的電話。這通電話受到調查，因為滑行時禁止使用手機。雖然如此，調查人員並未發現任何電話影響到航班的跡象。然而，片中完全沒有提及此事<ref name="Bustle (2016-09-09)"/>。另一方面，與該片不同的是，蘇倫柏格本人在事後從未對自己的決定感到懷疑<ref name="History vs. Hollywood">{{cite web |title=Sully (2016) |url=http://www.historyvshollywood.com/reelfaces/sully/ |work=History vs. Hollywood |accessdate=2017-10-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905052329/http://www.historyvshollywood.com/reelfaces/sully/ |archivedate=2017-09-05 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 相關事件 ==

包含美國航空公司和英國航空公司在內的幾家主要航空公司不願在飛機上放映《薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟》，美國航空公司表示，「我們覺得這部片可能會讓機上乘客感到不安」，而英國航空公司的發言人則說道「我們不放映那些劇情會讓乘客不安的電影」<ref name="The Independent (2016-11-24)">{{cite web |last1=Calder |first1=Simon |date=2016-11-24 |title=Should Sully, the film about 'The Miracle on the Hudson', be shown on flights? |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/sully-tom-hanks-emergency-landing-hudson-river-inflight-entertainment-british-airways-virgin-a7436466.html |work=''The Independent'' |accessdate=2018-05-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420031148/https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/sully-tom-hanks-emergency-landing-hudson-river-inflight-entertainment-british-airways-virgin-a7436466.html |archivedate=2018-04-20}}</ref>。不同於其他航空公司，[[維珍集團|維珍航空]]選擇在2017年1月放映該片<ref name="The Independent (2016-11-24)"/>。維珍航空表示，「安全始終是我們的第一任務，於是我們透過放映該片來表揚機組人員的精湛技術和貢獻」<ref name="The Independent (2016-11-24)"/>。

